Error: Error: "Failed To Establish A Connection To The Database. Connection Refused"

Solution: Step 1: Check your database credentials.

Make sure you have provided the correct database credentials in the Pterodactyl panel for your Minecraft server. If you are unsure about the database credentials, you can go back to your database and double-check it.

Step 2: Ensure that the database is running.

To check if the database is running, try connecting to it using the command line or GUI interface.
